data.description: Amazing all brick home! Just minutes from Concord Mills shopping and attractions!This home sits bold on the hill of a half acre corner lot. With new laminate floors through the main living space, the updated kitchen and bathrooms are sure to steal the show. Soft close cabinets and drawers throughout the kitchen makes for a seamless cooking experience. The open layout offers an additional flex space off the main living area perfect for an office, zoom room, library or just additional living space.
